            <div class="expectation-card">
              <div class="expectation-icon">üõ†Ô∏è</div>
              <h3>Early Access</h3>
              <p>Be first to know about new financial tools, visualization projects, and experimental art pieces.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="getting-started">
          <h2>Start Exploring</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">
            While you're here, dive into some of the most popular content that fellow subscribers love:
          </p>
          
          <div class="featured-content">
            <div class="content-item">
              <h3><a href="/blog/market-psychology-meets-algorithmic-beauty">Market Psychology Meets Algorithmic Beauty</a></h3>
              <p>Explore how emotional market patterns create unexpected visual art when rendered through code.</p>
              <span class="content-meta">12 min read ‚Ä¢ Featured</span>
            </div>
            
